did.unittitle: Undergraduate affairs, Yale College, records of the dean

repository.corpname: Yale University. Department of Manuscripts and Archives

did.abstract: The records consist of subject files maintained by the deans of Undergraduate Affairs and Student Affairs of Yale College, concerning the administration of undergraduate student life, student organizations, orientation programs, athletics, and student housing.

odd.head: General note
odd.p: Forms part of Yale Record Group 9-B (YRG 9-B), Records of deputy, associate, and assistant deans of Yale College.

accessrestrict.head: Conditions Governing Access
accessrestrict.p: Access to the records is restricted. See Collection Contents for details.

prefercite.head: Preferred Citation
prefercite.p: Undergraduate Affairs, Yale College, Records of the Dean (RU 95). Manuscripts and Archives, Yale University Library.

processinfo.head: Processing Information
processinfo.p: Yale University records are arranged and described at the accession level by the creating office. The University Archives creates collection level descriptive records, but typically does no further arrangement and description at the accession level.

scopecontent.head: Scope and Contents
scopecontent.p: The records consist of subject files maintained by the dean of Undergraduate Affairs and Student Affairs of Yale College, concerning the administration of undergraduate student life, student organizations, orientation programs, athletics, and student housing.

arrangement.head: Arrangement
arrangement.p: The records are arranged by accession.
